{"type":"article_comment","id":3314,"parentType":"article","parentId":860,"uid":4341,"contents":"膜改一段创普讲话：<br>\n<br>\n所以共和党的领导同志跟我讲话，说‘RNC都决定了，你来当总统候选人’，我说另请高明吧。我实在也不是谦虚，我一个纽约商界大佬怎么到华盛顿来了呢？但是，Paul Ryan同志讲‘大家已经研究决定了’，后来我就念了林肯总统的葛底斯堡演讲。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/2J2ax3a.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2J2ax3a.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/2J2ax3a.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-03","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":0}